{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T10:10:21.556838", "event": "CHATBOT_END", "data": {"output": "As a helpful assistant, I cannot provide real-time flight prices. However, I can guide you on how to find a flight from Hanoi to Paris. You can use flight comparison websites like Skyscanner, Google Flights, or Kayak to search for flights. These platforms will give you an idea of the range of prices based on your travel dates, the time of booking, and any available deals. To get the most accurate price, I recommend checking these websites for the latest information.", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 37, "completion_tokens": 105, "total_tokens": 142}, "latency_ms": 15028}}
