{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T10:11:18.331865", "event": "CHATBOT_END", "data": {"output": "As an AI, I don't have access to real-time databases or airline prices, but I can guide you on how to find the total cost of your flight from Hanoi to Paris with a 3-night stay using a promo code SUMMER. Here's a step-by-step process:\n\n1. Select your preferred airlines: Research and choose the airlines you'd like to fly with. Some popular options include Air France, Vietnam Airlines, or other international carriers.\n\n2. Compare prices: Use a flight comparison website like Skyscanner or Google Flights to compare the prices for your desired travel dates. Make sure you check the promo code details and if it applies to the airline you chose.\n\n3. Enter travel details: On the comparison website, enter your departure location (Hanoi) and your destination (Paris). Specify the desired stay duration (3 nights) if it influences the price.\n\n4. Apply promo code: Apply the promo code SUMMER to the flight search. Remember, not all promo codes are universal and may only apply to specific airlines.\n\n5. Calculate the cost: Once you've found the cheapest flights that meet your requirements, add up the costs of each flight (round-trip), and estimate the cost of your 3-night hotel stay in Paris. You may also need to factor in taxes and fees (airline, travel insurance, and potential luggage fees).\n\n6. Add all costs: To find the total cost, add the cost of flights and the hotel stay, including taxes and fees.\n\nKeep in mind that prices and promo codes may vary, so it's essential to check the latest prices and promo code validity. Once you have the costs, you can compare it with the promo code's discount to determine if you're getting the best deal.", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 59, "completion_tokens": 424, "total_tokens": 483}, "latency_ms": 56774}}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T10:11:18.332138", "event": "CHATBOT_START", "data": {"input": "Check flight from Ho Chi Minh to New York and hotel in New York.", "model": "Phi-3-mini-4k-instruct-q4.gguf"}}
{"timestamp": "2026-06-01T10:12:10.456419", "event": "CHATBOT_END", "data": {"output": "To help you find a flight from Ho Chi Minh to New York and a hotel in New York, I will provide you with information on how to do it. However, I can't book the flight or hotel for you. Here's how you can proceed:\n\n1. Finding a flight:\n\na. Airline websites: You can check airlines like United, American Airlines, Delta, or JetBlue, as they operate flights between Ho Chi Minh (code: SGN) and New York (code: JFK, EWR, LGA) regularly.\n\nb. Online travel agencies: Websites like Expedia, Kayak, or Skyscanner aggregate flights from various airlines and compare prices.\n\nc. Booking websites: Use popular sites like Booking.com or Hotels.com to search and compare flight options.\n\nDates, preferences (e.g., flight times, airlines, seats), and budget will affect the available options.\n\n2. Finding a hotel:\n\na. Online travel agencies: Use sites like Expedia, Booking.com, or Agoda to search for hotels in New York City.\n\nb. Hotel websites: Visit the websites of popular New York hotels such as Hilton, Marriott, or InterContinental to book a room.\n\nc. Review platforms: Check travel sites like TripAdvisor or Yelp for reviews and ratings on hotels in New York.\n\nWhen booking, consider factors such as price, location, amenities, and ratings.\n\nRemember to double-check the travel dates, flight times, and cancellation policies before finalizing your bookings.", "usage": {"prompt_tokens": 41, "completion_tokens": 367, "total_tokens": 408}, "latency_ms": 52124}}
